            <h1 class="text-[32px] font-serif mb-2" style="color: #FFFFFF;">《伤仲永》节选</h1>
            <p class="text-[14px] mb-10" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">宋 · 王安石</p>

            <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-[18px] font-serif leading-relaxed" style="color: #FFFFFF;">金溪民方仲永，世隶耕。</p>
                    <p class="text-[14px] mt-2 leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">金溪有个平民叫方仲永，家里世代以耕田为业。</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-[18px] font-serif leading-relaxed" style="color: #FFFFFF;">仲永生五年，未尝识书具。</p>
                    <p class="text-[14px] mt-2 leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">仲永长到五岁时，从没见过书写工具。</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-[18px] font-serif leading-relaxed" style="color: #FFFFFF;">忽啼求之，父异焉，借旁近与之。</p>
                    <p class="text-[14px] mt-2 leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">忽然有一天哭着要这些东西，父亲对此感到惊异，从邻近人家借来给他。</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-[18px] font-serif leading-relaxed" style="color: #FFFFFF;">即书诗四句，并自为其名。</p>
                    <p class="text-[14px] mt-2 leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">仲永立刻写了四句诗，并且自己题写了名字。</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-5" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);">
                <p class="text-[12px]" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">古文翻译 · 逐句对照</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 右侧内容区 -->
        <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col">
